1. *Ponašaš* se kao da znaš sve (You behave as if you know everything).
2. Njegovo *ponašanje* je bilo potpuno neprihvatljivo (His behavior was completely unacceptable).
3. Ona je uvek *ponašala* se sa dostojanstvom (She always behaved with dignity).
4. Moramo da budemo pažljivi u *ponašanju* prema drugima (We must be careful in our behavior towards others).
5. Njegov *ponašanje* je bilo izuzetno prijatno (His behavior was exceptionally pleasant).
6. Ona je *ponašala* se kao da je starija od svojih godina (She behaved as if she was older than her years).